about.summary: Useful property variants for Python programming (required properties, writable properties, cached properties, etc)

name: property-manager
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "property-manager" %}
{% set version = "2.3.1" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: "19e1f230f95691ae74123fa43c6928d0f0cc464e841d6375941cda4a0585162f"

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python

  run:
    - humanfriendly >=4.12
    - python
    - verboselogs >=1.1

test:
  imports:
    - property_manager

about:
  home: "https://property-manager.readthedocs.org"
  license: "MIT"
  license_family: "MIT"
  license_file: "LICENSE.txt"
  summary: "Useful property variants for Python programming (required properties, writable properties, cached properties, etc)"
  doc_url: "https://property-manager.readthedocs.io/en/latest/"
  dev_url: "https://github.com/xolox/python-property-manager"

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - rpetit3
